The authors conducted immunohistochemical analysis:
p16INK4a expression in SMG were significantly reduced by ADF (p < 0.01);
Expression levels of anti-apoptotic molecules BCL-2, BCL-XL, and MCL-1 in SMG were decreased by ADF;
ADF decreased NLRP3 inflammasome expression level and, consequently, its products (IL-1β and IL-18).
